{"tid":915268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【比特幣崩盤】期貨跌破4200美元 礦機被當廢鐵斷斤賣","createTime":"2018-11-24T23:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T09:48:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"44d2420096cef4bbef2cfce9e0d4a065bfbb07f4","tid":915268,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T23:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181124/large/1543038986_9c2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F1543038986_9c2b.jpg&h=7731ad32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加密虛擬貨幣跌入大熊市，比特幣期貨昨日跌破4,200美元，連帶拖累掘礦機亦變得一文不值。有中國網民近日拍片看到，數百台礦機猶如廢鐵般被棄置垃圾堆，由於比特幣價不停下跌，已不足以抵消掘比特幣消耗的電力成本，部分中小型礦場已無奈倒閉，礦機就被人當廢鐵斷斤賣。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣自八月開始大跌，拖累掘礦機晶片商Nvidia業績不乎預期，股價大跌28%，CME比特幣期貨BTC 1月合約收市大跌200美元，跌幅超過4.57%，報4175美元，創即月合約收盤紀錄新低，本週累跌逾23.04%；而CBOE比特幣期貨XBT 1月合約收跌185美元，跌約4.23%，報4,190美元，也創即月合約收市紀錄新低，本週累跌約22.66%。<br />\n<br />\nBloomberg Intelligence認為虛擬貨幣正步入寒冬，比特幣更有可能進一步下跌至1,500美元，較現價再跌6成多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181124/58952396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58952396&d=8zFlkMM53qITZ6U1f%2FK3gFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=c00f9a80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58952396&h=f3cfb2df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181124/58952396</a>"},{"pid":"38bc0a9f74f1a97f334502313d9d5b7f4fe4e47b","tid":915268,"uid":39693,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"啱啦，啲卡都係時候跌返價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等到蚊都瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">抵啦屌</span>"